{"id": "1409821028594614302", "channel_id": "1409821028594614302", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼，今日发布～欢迎大家收听、下载及分享～如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n忘却前夜OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼\n燃烧吧，燃烧吧，将属于你的一切，尽数燃烧吧。\n然后在那无尽的烈火中，开启你和世界的葬礼吧！\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST：\"Kathigu-Ra EP: Funeral in Flames\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\nMorimens OST：\"Kathigu-Ra EP: Funeral in Flames\"\nBurn, burn, let all that is yours be consumed in flames.\nThen, in the boundless fire, let the funeral for you and this world commence!\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T08:45:26.425000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🎉", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "❤️‍🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1409821030037586000", "filename": "OST--.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2940746, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821030037586000/OST--.jpg?ex=69ccdb26&is=69cb89a6&hm=99f638c5f4a0a6fe9946b0822d90c2b0a26b0761f47c886e67543ba2e40cc6fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409821028594614302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1409821186019561483", "channel_id": "1409821028594614302", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01.篝火温憩-Fireside Respite-**\n\n把烦恼暂时放下，让疲倦快快远离。\n让我们在温暖的篝火旁，稍稍休息一下吧。\nLet worries fade and weariness drift away on the smoke.\nHere by the warming flames, we rest awhile.", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T08:46:03.958000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1409821185038094366", "filename": "1-Fireside_Respite-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1686866, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821185038094366/1-Fireside_Respite-.jpg?ex=69ccdb4b&is=69cb89cb&hm=d56d9140f04cad60946c0dde10555a361cbff1ae237944e5f626fe71a34d61d6&"}, {"id": "1409821185444806666", "filename": "1_-Fireside_Respite-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 2524844, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821185444806666/1_-Fireside_Respite-.mp3?ex=69ccdb4b&is=69cb89cb&hm=58e687af2d5e05ee6ac1346ecb1f3a159697149162d9d545294cdce62dd0e05a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409821028594614302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1409821305926057984", "channel_id": "1409821028594614302", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02.四十亿年的再会-Four Billion Years' Reunion-**\n\n群星间永不熄灭的存在再次睁开双眼，将不朽的力量投射至这颗浑浊、污秽却无比蔚蓝的星球，\n与那四十亿年前，遮天蔽日的太阳降临时一模一样。\nFrom the eternal stars, the ever-burning Presence opens Its eyes once more, pouring undying power upon this turbid, tainted, yet beautifully azure world: a planet as radiantly blue as when the sky-devouring sun first descended upon it, four billion years ago.", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T08:46:32.546000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1409821305100042320", "filename": "2_-Four_Billion_Years_Reunion-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 4104044, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821305100042320/2_-Four_Billion_Years_Reunion-.mp3?ex=69ccdb68&is=69cb89e8&hm=6e8406720255ed1eb836d2c739502cc16f68e6d0d4044043c3afdb9655ba5ffe&"}, {"id": "1409821305590644797", "filename": "2-Four_Billion_Years_Reunion-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1688816, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821305590644797/2-Four_Billion_Years_Reunion-.jpg?ex=69ccdb68&is=69cb89e8&hm=070e9bba6449173d22a7d4b53ed1400f97f907171d26bd088b24a6b842fbfac3&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409821028594614302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1409821497693962250", "channel_id": "1409821028594614302", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03.燃烧一切的拂晓-The Dawn That Burns All-**\n\n“我说过了，无论以哪种方式，我都要将大家带回家。”\n“我会燃烧属于我的一切，然后……”\n“用这来自群星的业火，将这虚假、污秽、混沌的世界燃烧殆尽！”\n“我以凯蒂古拉之名宣告！”\n“天将拂晓！”\n“I have sworn to bring everyone home, by any means necessary.\nSo I will burn away all that I am…\n…and with the karmic fire of the stars, I will scour this false, foul, and chaotic world clean!\nBy my name, Kathigu-Ra!\nNow I bring the dawn!”", "timestamp": "2025-08-26T08:47:18.267000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1409821496469098496", "filename": "3-The_Dawn_That_Burns_All-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1704911, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821496469098496/3-The_Dawn_That_Burns_All-.jpg?ex=69ccdb95&is=69cb8a15&hm=0c0a9b23fa545134db73d966f268845904be0c80c10dd7ada240c9efab7990e9&"}, {"id": "1409821496939122728", "filename": "3_-The_Dawn_That_Burns_All-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 43882966, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1409821028594614302/1409821496939122728/3_-The_Dawn_That_Burns_All-.wav?ex=69ccdb96&is=69cb8a16&hm=ed1f2c99b6d574feddda2fedd185e04bdf4f0b161d8b634851bd1813c92f3b26&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1409821028594614302", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：凯蒂古拉EP·烈火的葬礼", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
